Class main.cell.Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.cell.Cell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    main.helper.Locatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    main.cell.RedCell, main.cell.SickCell, main.cell.WhiteCell

    public abstract class main.cell.Cell
extends java.lang.Object
implements main.helper.Locatable
    Abstract class which defines a cell. All cells can be attacked by Viruses, but different cells have different functions. This class contains very basic methods that pertain to all cells, as well as several abstract methods such as update(), setHealth(), etc.
